dio': 0, 'cache_read': 1024}, 'output_token_details': {'audio': 0, 'reasoning': 0}}), ToolMessage(content='Saved', name='create_gmail_draft', tool_call_id='call_Nz7kMwI4RG9SPP4qforsOVCv'), AIMessage(content="I have drafted an email for you that includes recent papers on advancements in machine learning. You can review and send it when you're ready. Here’s the content:\n\n---\n\n**Subject:** Recent Papers on Machine Learning Advancements\n\nDear [Recipient's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to share some recent papers that delve into advancements in machine learning, which I believe you might find interesting:\n\n1. **Changing Data Sources in the Age of Machine Learning for Official Statistics**\n   - This paper discusses the challenges and potential pitfalls of integrating machine learning into official statistics, particularly focusing on the dangers of over-reliance on changing data sources. It provides a checklist to mitigate these risks and maintain the integrity of machine learning-based statistics.\n\n2. **DOME: Recommendations for Supervised Machine Learning Validation in Biology**\n   - This paper critiques the current state of supervised machine learning validation in biology, highlighting the lack of universal standards. It emphasizes the need for a more structured approach to ensure reliable algorithm performance and discusses the limitations of existing methods.\n\n3. **Learning Curves for Decision Making in Supervised Machine Learning: A Survey**\n   - This survey examines the drawbacks of using learning curves in supervised machine learning, questioning their reliability in decision-making processes. It reviews various models and highlights the challenges in accurately assessing algorithm performance through learning curves.\n\nIf you would like to discuss any of these papers further or need additional information, feel free to reach out.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Your Contact Information]\n\n---\n\nLet me know if you need any changes or if you would like to send it!", additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 328, 'prompt_tokens': 1680, 'total_tokens': 2008, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': 0}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': 0, 'cached_tokens': 1024}, 'input_tokens': 0, 'output_tokens': 0, 'input_tokens_details': None}, 'model_name': 'gpt-4o-mini', 'system_fingerprint': 'fp_eb37e061ec', 'finish_reason': 'stop', 'logprobs': None}, id='run-e67e4b14-da69-49e3-9630-75451e1b3492-0', usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 1680, 'output_tokens': 328, 'total_tokens': 2008, 'input_token_details': {'audio': 0, 'cache_read': 1024}, 'output_token_details': {'audio': 0, 'reasoning': 0}})]
